{"word":"Hur","slug":"hur","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Hur</b> <a href=\"#/H2354\">H2354</a> <br/> 1. An Israelite who assisted in supporting Moses' hands during battle<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=17&verse=10'>Exo 17:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=17&verse=12'>Exo 17:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=24&verse=14'>Exo 24:14</a><br/> 2. A son of Caleb<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=31&verse=2'>Exo 31:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=35&verse=30'>Exo 35:30</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=38&verse=22'>Exo 38:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=2&verse=20'>1Ch 2:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=1&verse=5'>2Ch 1:5</a><br/> 3. A king of Midian<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=31&verse=8'>Num 31:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=13&verse=21'>Jos 13:21</a><br/> 4. Called Ben Hur, an officer of Solomon's commissary<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=4&verse=8'>1Ki 4:8</a><br/> 5. Father of Caleb<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=2&verse=50'>1Ch 2:50</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=4&verse=4'>1Ch 4:4</a><br/> 6. A son of Judah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=4&verse=1'>1Ch 4:1</a><br/> 7. A ruler<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=3&verse=9'>Neh 3:9</a>"}]}